{"tid":1041791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"邊個咁賤格搵條大陸生滋狗同香港變革者配種再同佢講係日本種？","createTime":"2019-03-01T06:01:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T13:53:06.000Z","uid":11703,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cacfa32a898aceef39a72f26630d09805b7b9564","tid":1041791,"uid":11703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T06:01:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2afb7372c827cf005c7e6aa1e0ffd0a2c1383e2e","tid":1041791,"uid":198583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T06:03:32.000Z","msg":"你老母😂😂"},{"pid":"fcaa30e9e39ce41722dd9a9a40f3919b88897c38","tid":1041791,"uid":130695,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"cacfa32a898aceef39a72f26630d09805b7b9564","tid":1041791,"uid":11703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T06:01:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T06:19:04.000Z","msg":"完全封鎖左，件垃圾仲未死咩？<br />\n我見佢老母日日吊係廣場任人騎<br />\n個老豆仲笑哂口咁一蚊一蚊咁執<br />\n仲有啲主人帶哂動物黎<br />\n掉低張100 哇 個場面幾震撼<br />\n然後佢老豆仲問個主人可唔可以屌埋佢<br />\n買一送一咁喎<br />\n點知個主人叫佢奶返乾淨滴落地啲精同屎<br />\n佢老豆仲口upup 話呢鋪發達啦<br />\n我咁大個人都未見過泥沙地都變鏡面<br />\n呢件垃圾聽講係之前唔知點生出黎既<br />\n我都幾同情佢嫁，日日靠奶老母個臭閪<br />\n同老豆爭食 咁都養得大<br />\n果然中国多奇人"},{"pid":"544e8fc505b69e5838fd880f30b98b4a12ed6274","tid":1041791,"uid":130695,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cacfa32a898aceef39a72f26630d09805b7b9564","tid":1041791,"uid":11703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T06:01:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T06:20:45.000Z","msg":"佢有可能真係有日本種嫁<br />\n咩都屌過佢老母<br />\n佢又靠奶老母啲臭閪汁大<br />\n打亂種係指佢嫁啦"},{"pid":"c765830fed3eb137a5f8d7fa434070d5cdb6b74f","tid":1041791,"uid":11703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"544e8fc505b69e5838fd880f30b98b4a12ed6274","tid":1041791,"uid":130695,"like":3,"dis